name: Nature Art Nudes by Damian Diviny

metadata.name: Slow Wave
metadata.description:
Slowing down time and capturing a small fraction of it.

One of the many beautiful scenes created with Cheyanne in this ancient landscape. 

This one was captured as the waves were breaking on the boulders just in front of Cheyanne. It was the last one before a larger wave soaked her, ending our shots for this setup.

The location is Phillip Island, Victoria, Australia.
